# UPMEM Swap - .gitignore 
# Essential: src/, simulator/src/, scripts/*.py, images
# Ignore: build artifacts, logs, autogenerated docs

## Build & Compilation
build/
*.o
*.a
*.so
*.dylib
*.out
CMakeCache.txt
CMakeFiles/
cmake_install.cmake
Makefile

## Binaries
swap_sim
benchmark_*
test_*
dpu_tasklets
host

## IDE & Editors
.vscode/
.idea/
*.swp
*.swo
*~
.DS_Store

## Python
__pycache__/
*.py[cod]
*$py.class
*.egg-info/
.pytest_cache/

## Logs & Temporary Files
*.log
*.tmp
*.bak
*.orig
*.txt
*.jpg
*.png
*.pdf
*.csv

## Data & Results (keep ONLY final article figures)
results_*.csv
benchmark_results.csv
analysis_report.txt
simulator_dump.txt
simulator/results/*.log
simulator/results/*.csv
!simulator/results/Figure*.png
!simulator/results/Figure*_Legend.txt

## Prototypes & WIP
Makefilemake
*.backup
*_old.*

## Misc
prompter.sh
project_context.txt
quick_install.sh.bak
